flowRoot.flowPara: Banners are displayed using the same logic as now:
* One banner is displayed at once.
* If several banners are scheduled to be displayed at the same time, they are queued and displayed in sequence.
* Hovering over a banner expands it to reveal more body text, along with any actions it contains.
* Banners are not displayed when the time and date drop down is open.
* Urgent banners are displayed in expanded mode by default, and must be acknowledged to dismiss.

flowRoot.flowPara: * Updated banner layout aims to be consistent with the layout of notifications in the revised, list-based Message Tray.
* Buttons have a different layout, and are placed flush t to the edge of the banner itself.
* There are no close buttons on banners
Except for the last change, these modifications are not essential to the redesign.
